Answer.RepaymentChannels:
You can transfer the amount to CUB's repayment account through NAPAS 24/7 or MoMo e-wallet: 
<span class="font-bold ">1. Through NAPAS 24/7:</span> Go to CUB Vietnam App -> choose Repay Method is <span class="font-bold ">"Bank"</span>, check your payment account number at Cathay United Bank -> make payment at your Bank's app;
<span class="font-bold ">2. Through MoMo E-Wallet:</span> Go to CUB Vietnam App, choose Repay Method is <span class="font-bold ">"E-Wallet"</span>, click <span class="font-bold ">"Lead to MoMo"</span> -> MoMo E-Wallet will show the detail of amount to be paid and you can make payment directly on MoMo E-Wallet.
